### Story 3.6 seed-driven demo contract
# Requires seeded admin token and existing category/option group IDs from seed data.
# Proves product can be created with Size/Topping groups and each successful mutation bumps menu_version.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@token = replace-with-admin-jwt
@categoryId = replace-with-seeded-category-uuid
@sizeGroupId = replace-with-seeded-size-option-group-uuid
@toppingGroupId = replace-with-seeded-topping-option-group-uuid

### Observe current menu version
GET {{baseUrl}}/menu
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create product with Size/Topping option groups; expect 201 and menu_version increment
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Demo cà phê sữa",
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "priceVnd": 35000,
  "isActive": true,
  "sortOrder": 10,
  "optionGroupIds": ["{{sizeGroupId}}", "{{toppingGroupId}}"]
}

### Update product; expect menu_version increment and snapshots untouched
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/replace-with-created-product-id
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "priceVnd": 39000, "optionGroupIds": ["{{sizeGroupId}}"] }

### Tạm tắt product instead of deleting if it may be sold again; expect menu_version increment
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/replace-with-created-product-id/toggle-active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "isActive": false }

### Delete only if no historical order_items; expect 204 and menu_version increment
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/replace-with-created-product-id
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### If product has historical order_items, expect 409 product-in-use with Vietnamese guidance
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/replace-with-in-use-product-id
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
